<br>
Benefits:<br>
* Raidwindow option<br>
* Fast travel - You click on portal and u're there, no more long ass time sink waiting for a portal to activate.<br>
* Some good spells u can find in the library<br>
* Some easy quest that yields decent equipment.<br>
* Great place to bind / make as base of operations<br>
* You can bank / sell (and Nexus is just a portal away)<br>
<br>
Bad thing:<br>
* Unless a group is REALLY desperate no one would really take on a level 52 player.<br>
* Mobs hits REALLY hard. The weakest mobs in Tier 1 planes hit for at least 180s.<br>
* Mobs that most people will be killing hits for 250-400s range.<br>
* Lowest mobs are around level 46. Most boss mobs are in the level 60-70 range. Regular mobs are in the 50-60 range.<br>
<br>
